---
import Page from "../../layouts/Page.astro";
---

<Page title="Bots | Botify Life" description="Create, manage, and deploy bots easily with Botify Life.">
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-16 px-4">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-blue-700 mb-6 text-center">
      Effortless Bot Creation with Botify Life
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Creating, customizing, and deploying bots is seamless, smooth, and reliable with Botify Life. Our platform lets you add new bots in just a few clicks—no coding required. Enjoy intuitive controls, robust integrations, and real-time monitoring for all your automation needs.
    </p>
    <p class="text-base text-blue-600 font-medium text-center mb-8">
      Integrate with your website easily
    </p>
    <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
      <li class="bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-6 shadow flex flex-col items-center text-center">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-plus-circle text-3xl text-blue-500 mb-3"></i>
        <span class="font-semibold text-blue-700 mb-1">Simple to Add</span>
        <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Add new bots to your workflow in seconds with our user-friendly interface.</span>
      </li>
      <li class="bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-6 shadow flex flex-col items-center text-center">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-wave-square text-3xl text-blue-500 mb-3"></i>
        <span class="font-semibold text-blue-700 mb-1">Smooth Automation</span>
        <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Automate tasks and processes effortlessly, with smooth integration across your tools.</span>
      </li>
      <li class="bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-6 shadow flex flex-col items-center text-center">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check text-3xl text-blue-500 mb-3"></i>
        <span class="font-semibold text-blue-700 mb-1">Reliable Results</span>
        <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Count on Botify Life for consistent, reliable bot performance—every time.</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <div class="text-center">
      <a href="/signup" class="inline-block px-8 py-3 rounded-xl bg-blue-600 text-white font-semibold shadow hover:bg-blue-700 transition">
        Start Building Bots Now
      </a>
    </div>
  </main>
</Page>